@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Registro de Novo Usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "confirmarSenha": "senha123"
}

### Registro com Email Duplicado (erro esperado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Teste Duplicado",
  "email": "admin@studiuzen.com",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "confirmarSenha": "senha123"
}

### Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@studiuzen.com",
  "senha": "admin123"
}

### Login Usuário Comum (após criar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "senha": "senha123"
}

### Verify Token (usar token obtido do login acima)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Listar Todos os Usuários (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI

### Deletar Usuário (Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/2
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI

### Atualizar Status do Usuário (Admin Only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/2/status
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ativo": false
}

### Erro - Login com senha inválida
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@studiuzen.com",
  "senha": "senhaerrada"
}

### Erro - Acesso sem token
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users

### Erro - Acesso como usuário comum (não admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_USUARIO_COMUM_AQUI
